# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CODEOWNERS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Defines who is automatically requested to review PRs that touch specific
# files or directories. GitHub enforces CODEOWNERS approval before merge when
# branch protection is enabled.
#
# FORMAT
#   <path-pattern>   @github-username-or-team
#
# MAINTENANCE
#   Update owners when team members change roles or leave.
#   To require CODEOWNERS review on main, enable it in:
#   Settings → Branches → main → "Require review from Code Owners"
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

